    <item>
      <title>宝马因火灾隐患在华召回近 70 万辆汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/bmw-recalls-almost-700-000-cars-in-china-on-fire-safety-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马汽车公司 (BMW AG) 因冷却泵缺陷在中国召回近 70 万辆汽车，这对于已深陷其他车辆故障泥潭的德国汽车制造商而言，无疑是雪上加霜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/bmw-recalls-almost-700-000-cars-in-china-on-fire-safety-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 14:50:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称白宫团队将访问基辅讨论计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/white-house-team-to-visit-kyiv-to-discuss-plan-zelenskiy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，美国白宫团队将很快访问乌克兰，就其所谓的“胜利计划”提供反馈，该计划概述了他结束俄罗斯入侵的愿景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/white-house-team-to-visit-kyiv-to-discuss-plan-zelenskiy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 14:44:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行预计 2025 年市政债券销售额将创纪录达到 5200 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/bank-of-america-sees-record-520-billion-of-muni-sales-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市政债券市场最大承销商的策略师预测，对于州和地方政府债务银行家来说，今年将会非常忙碌。]]></description>
